                  <span class="">这一页介绍可证伪，即弗洛伊德发觉自己的解释没有被患者接受时，就说患者有很强的阻抗，是患者拒绝承认自身的症状。 the experience of reflectionis the only criterion for the corroboration or failure of hypotheses. If it does not come about, there is still an alternative: either the interpretation is false(that is, the theory or its application to a given case) or, to the contrary, the resistances, whi...</span>
