                  <span class="">分析性的观点只有当它们被分析者作为认识接受之后，才对分析者有价值 英译版： analytic insights possess validity for the analyst only after they have been acceptedas knowledge by the analysand himself. 英译版显然说得更清楚：分析师认为这个解释有validity，是因为他自己接受了这个观点 For the empirical accuracy of general interpretations depends not on controlled observation and subsequent communication...</span>
