                  <span class="">作者终于开始评论弗洛伊德 The energy-distribution model only creates the semblance that psychoanalytic statements are about measurable transformations of energy. Not a single statement about quantitative relations derived from the conception of instinctual economics has ever been tested experimentally. 弗的能量模型(力比多)在讲能量描述，但并没有实证的研究 中译： 受到了实验检验的唯一陈述 254页： ...</span>
