              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">弗洛伊德认为人会自我欺骗，使得非言语表达和言语表达相一致。 The subject must deceive itself about these non-verbal expressions that are not coordinated with linguistic expression. 220页，弗洛伊德认为，症状是一种语言，是内在冲突导致的。 Nevertheless, the symptoms are part of intentional structures: the ongoing text of everyday language games is broken through not by external influences but by int...</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2017-05-10 13:16</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <p>弗洛伊德认为人会自我欺骗，使得非言语表达和言语表达相一致。</p><blockquote>The subject must deceive itself about these non-verbal expressions that are not coordinated with linguistic expression.</blockquote><p>220页，弗洛伊德认为，症状是一种语言，是内在冲突导致的。</p><blockquote>Nevertheless, the symptoms are part of intentional structures: the ongoing text of everyday language games is broken through not by external influences but by internal disturbances.</blockquote><p>中译：</p><blockquote>记录我们日常语言活动的原文，不是被外部影响，而是被内部干扰破坏</blockquote><p>显然这个翻译没有明白disturbances是什么，也不知道the ongoing text是什么</p><p>-</p><p>222页开始介绍梦，梦如同症状，但不是病理的症状；梦的第一层是dream facade</p><p>稽查这个词，其实是resistance，再次反映翻译对精神分析一无所知</p>
